flowchart TD
    Start[Enter Phase 3] --> Epoch[Epoch 1 to max_epochs]
    Epoch --> Crit[Critique pass parallel batched]
    Crit --> Routing[Route objections per item]
    Routing -->|critical| Edit[SME edit + reverify cascade]
    Routing -->|non-critical| Rebut[SME rebut_objections batched]
    Rebut -->|ACCEPT| Edit
    Rebut -->|REBUT or DEFER| Stay[objection stays open]
    Edit -->|passes| Resolved[resolved]
    Edit -->|fails| Rejected[item rejected]
    Resolved --> Conv[Convergence check]
    Stay --> Conv
    Rejected --> Conv
    Conv -->|crit or high open| Epoch
    Conv -->|none open| CP3[Checkpoint 3]
